I zipped it up using 7zip (free download from http://www.7-zip.org/download.html) using ultra settings, to compress the files in half so it downloads a lot quicker. unzipped it is 250MB, zipped it is 111MB.

Please remember to seed and say thanks!
Will it work on KAOS version?

Yes, it should work on every version, since it replaces the core files with the updates. However, I do recommend the Razor 1911 version because I can ensure that version is stable. You can find it here on TPB, just do a search.
